M_GOJPdTfY-ncAU5Fdw">Tây Thi - 西施</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0-Ch%C3%BA/author-VHS_JvG4NANbuv3vgzgaQQ">Lư Chú</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%C3%B9ng-Duy%C3%AAn-K%E1%BB%B7/Th%C3%A1i-tang-t%E1%BB%AD-k%E1%BB%B3-09/poem-xQbAS3msLllmTtVElPGw6g">Thái tang tử kỳ 09 - 采桑子其九</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%C3%B9ng-Duy%C3%AAn-K%E1%BB%B7/author-NkGwR6r3M3j5cQXaNNhfvQ">Phùng Duyên Kỷ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Th%C3%A2m/V%C3%A3n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-thi%E1%BA%BFu-b%E1%BA%A3o-Nh%E1%BB%AF-Chu/poem-uFNjdBO-q8fb8v0AFa7EMA">Vãn Vương thiếu bảo Nhữ Chu - 挽王少保汝舟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Th%C3%A2m/author-TJAW-7LZED05XHYEd7a5-A">Trần Đình Thâm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/V%E1%BB%8B-Xuy%C3%AAn-%C4%91i%E1%BB%81n-gia/poem-B1fIrcRGboNPc0AFY_NFhQ">Vị Xuyên điền gia - 渭川田家</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/author-9f1Hth0gmM_PXzGNXg5Fog">Vương Duy</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-%E1%BB%90c/%E1%BB%B6-tu%C3%BD/poem-t-WQqz6RAeIW0Dxc11HHzw">Ỷ tuý - 倚醉</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-%E1%BB%90c/author-wyu82iSv-bH9msUkq5vWDQ">Hàn Ốc</a>)<br></div>	</div>
